<title>USA: Action Industries to sell assets.</title>
<headline>Action Industries to sell assets.</headline>
<dateline>PITTSBURGH, Pa. 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Action Industries Inc said Wednesday it signed a nonbinding letter of intent dated August 30 to sell its inventory and related intellectual property associated with Action's Powerhouse (Replenishment) Business and Promotional Business to Mazel Co LP.</p>
<p>Mazel is based in Deleware.</p>
<p>The letter is subject to approval by Action's board.</p>
<p>Action's Promotional-related assets will be sold subject to approval by Action's shareholders, which should take between 60 and 90 days, a statement from the company said.</p>
